  "body": "# ðŸš€ Feature Request\r\n\r\n### Description\r\n\r\nSimilar to this idea https://github.com/prysmaticlabs/prysm/issues/5574 where we are able to change the log level verbosity, users have requested the ability to change other flag parameters. \r\n\r\nThe specific user request was to be able to adjust the p2p max peer count.\r\n\r\n### Describe the solution you'd like\r\n\r\nAn endpoint that allows users to change some or all flag values without having to restart their process.\r\n\r\n### Describe alternatives you've considered\r\n\r\nNone yet.\r\n",
